title: Dodi in the Wind
description:
Written by Ryan Hunter
Starring: Kelly Hudson, Dan Hodapp, Avery Monsen, Langan Kingsley, Jonathan Marballi, Kristy Lopez-Bernal, Kerry O'Brien, Ryan Hunter, Alene Latimer, Zack Phillips, Jon Bershad

Directed by Jim Santangeli

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, January 6, 2014.

Filmed by Matthew Alston and Curtis Raye.
Edited by Curtis Raye.
